This fun, Banana-Leaf-print DII 100% POLYESTER TABLECLOTH FOR OUTDOOR USE (60 Round, Seats 4 People) is an outdoor tablecloth that can be used indoors--the fabric looks that good!  Although it's 100% polyester, the fabric feels somewhat similar to the fabric in DIIs traditional 100% cotton tablecloths.  The fabric is spill-proof because it is very tightly woven from polyester thread.  It doesn't feel at all like plastic or oilcloth.

The bold Banana Leaf pattern is printed on, so the reverse side of the tablecloth is white.  The construction is excellent, with a nicely turned and topstitched hem.  The tablecloth is machine washable.

This is a magnificent and beautifully written book set in post WWII Germany. Three incredible women, all widows, and their children brought together and each with their own strengths as well as flaws, learn to survive in the terrible aftermath of war. Gripping from the first pages to the end. Fantastic and well-researched historical fiction. I highly recommend this book.

Way, way to subtle and dull film.  I totally understand why some critics called it boring.  It was.  Worst was there was no chemistry between Steve Carell and Keira Knightley which is crucial in a film like this that is depressing and goes no where.  You need something for the fans to hang on to.  Poor film, not entertaining.  This is one to pass on.

I did a lot of research before buying my rowing machine, and I think this is the best one made.  It is not inexpensive, but it is worth every dollar.  This is quality all the way.  Rowing is a total body exercise, as well as being aerobic, so a rowing machine beats a treadmill, stationary bike, or elliptical machine hands down.  You will love this machine.

Andrea has an intense emotional and powerful time a head of her. When she makes it home to her brother Bobby she isn't prepared for his best friend Andy.
Andy makes her forget what she is running from and believing in love and being happy again. Will they be able to survive what they are up for? You don't want to miss this powerful and captivating romance about second chances.

I voluntarily reviewed this ARC.
This is an awesome key holder.  It really does a good job of organizing keys!!!

I love Mia as an author. I love how strong she develops the love that her characters share. Just when you think she can't top her last story she proves you wrong by creating an even more heartwarming love story.

Archer is the ultimate hero. You will root for him from the very beginning! He is the definition of strength..He is kind...He is pure of heart. This story kind of reminded me of Beauty and the Beast, ultimately one of my favorite love stories.

I have to believe that there are people in this world, who get an ounce of money and control and let it all go to their head, therefore, this book is so real life it makes you wonder if anyone is ever truly safe. Excellent book!

Looks good but it's smaller than I'd expected for the price. It includes a Lex Luthor figure that can be used to  provide various actions . The eyes light up and open . The batteries are included which is a plus.  You or your child will definitely want to add more  characters , both additional villains and heroes for  more enjoyable play.  The Imiginext line is geared toward ages 3 to 8 . I suspect that by age 8 there are other DC  character lines more age appropriate but these are great for the younger kids.

I love this series so much! They just keep getting better! Reading the growth of the characters and the love they have for each other makes my heart happy!  One of the best things is the action that takes place. Ms. Bennett never fails to supply heart stopping thrills.
